==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pullback
<hw>Pull"back`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
which holds back, or causes to recede; a drawback; a
hindrance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Arch)</fld> <def>The iron hook fixed to a casement
to pull it shut, or to hold it party open at a fixed point.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pulldevil</ent>⟦br⟧
